CLIENT_NAME_INFO: Name of the application to be presented to the End-User.
CONTACT_INFO: Array of e-mail addresses of people responsible for this application
REDIRECT_URI_INFO: Array of Redirection URI values used by the application
LOGO_URI_INFO: URL that references a logo for the Client application
POLICY_URI_INFO: URL that the Relying Party Client provides to the End-User to read about the how the profile data will be used
TOS_URI_INFO: URL that the Relying Party Client provides to the End-User to read about the Relying Party's terms of service
CLIENT_URI_INFO: URL of the home page of the Client.
CLIENT_PREFERENCE_INFO: Edit the preference like preferred authentication method
ACCESS_TOKEN_GENERATION: Algorithm chosen to generate the token
REFRESH_TOKEN_EXPIRATION_TIME_SECONDS: Reference token expiration time in seconds
